column1: IF ccr_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
IF ccr_tha_d is MF 2 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF  THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_sa_thb_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_sb_oh_f_d is MF 1 AND ccr_thf_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
